\[p(\bm{f}|\bm{X},\bm{y})=\frac{p(\bm{y}|\bm{X},\bm{f})p(\bm{f})}{ p(\bm{y}|\bm{X})}=\mathcal{N}_{N}(\bm{f};\bm{\mu},\bm{S}),\] (18)

