\[\bm{\mu}=\sigma^{-2}\left(\bm{K}^{-1}+\sigma^{-2}\bm{I}_{N}\right) ^{-1}\bm{y}\in\mathbb{R}^{N},\qquad\quad\bm{S}=\left(\bm{K}^{-1}+\sigma^{-2} \bm{I}_{N}\right)^{-1}\in\mathbb{R}^{N\times N}.\]

