\[p(\bm{f}^{\prime}|\bm{X},\bm{y})=\int p(\bm{f}^{\prime}|\bm{f})p (\bm{f}|\bm{X},\bm{y})=\mathcal{N}_{M}(\bm{f}^{\prime};\bm{\mu}^{\prime},\bm{S} ^{\prime}),\] (19)

